programme.title: Workshop Vagabond Vacations
programme.desc: JONA ​​and JC, our faithful vloggers, continue to surprise us! This time, they organize crazy photoshoots all over the world! Incredible models, dreamscapes, international photographers... With their touch of humor that we all know well, they make us live their adventures as directors, photographers and lovers... In this 2nd episode in Costa Rica, let's ride an old school bus for a colorful photoshoot ! And take some gorgeous shots in an infinity pool...
